text: Tanuchitina is an extinct genus of chitinozoans. It was described by Jansonius in 1964.Tanuchitina at ChitDB: Chitinozoans of Baltica. ==Species== * Tanuchitina anticostiensis (Achab, 1977) * Tanuchitina bergstroemi Laufeld, 1967 * Tanuchitina tallinnensis Grahn, 1984 ==References== Category:Prehistoric marine animals Category:Fossil taxa described in 1964 Category:Paleozoic life of Quebec
title: Tanuchitina
